  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Redesign Program Cards Layout on Programs Page\n\nUpdate the programs page to display program cards in a more compact, three-column grid layout with consistent spacing.\n\nRequirements:\n- Reduce the size of each program-card component to fit three cards per row\n- Ensure the three-column layout is responsive and works across different screen sizes\n- Add consistent vertical spacing between rows of cards\n- Add consistent horizontal spacing (gap) between cards in each row\n- Maintain proper alignment and prevent cards from stretching unevenly\n- Ensure card content (images, text, buttons) scales appropriately with the smaller card size\n- Verify that all card content remains readable and accessible at the reduced size\n- Test on mobile/tablet to ensure responsive breakpoints work correctly (likely stacking to 1-2 columns on smaller screens)",
  "title": "Implement responsive three-column grid for program cards",
